            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3E2%20Samuel%2015%3A23-16%3A23%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_15_23%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%2223%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E23%3C%2Fspan%3EEveryone%20cried%20loudly%20as%20the%20king%20and%20his%20followers%20passed%20by.%20They%20crossed%20the%20Kidron%20Valley%20and%20then%20went%20out%20toward%20the%20wilderness.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_15_24%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%2224%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E24%3C%2Fspan%3EZadok%20and%20all%20the%20Levites%20also%20came%20along%2C%20carrying%20the%20Ark%20of%20the%20Covenant%20of%20God.%20They%20set%20down%20the%20Ark%20of%20God%2C%20and%20Abiathar%20offered%20sacrifices%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E15%3A24%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3EAbiathar%20went%20up.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20until%20everyone%20had%20passed%20out%20of%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_15_25%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%2225%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E25%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20king%20instructed%20Zadok%20to%20take%20the%20Ark%20of%20God%20back%20into%20the%20city.%20%26%23x201C%3BIf%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20sees%20fit%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20David%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3Bhe%20will%20bring%20me%20back%20to%20see%20the%20Ark%20and%20the%20Tabernacle%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E15%3A25%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Eand%20his%20dwelling%20place.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20again.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_15_26%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%2226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E26%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20if%20he%20is%20through%20with%20me%2C%20then%20let%20him%20do%20what%20seems%20best%20to%20him.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_15_27%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%2227%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E27%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20king%20also%20told%20Zadok%20the%20priest%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BLook%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E15%3A27a%3C%2Fspan%3E%20As%20in%20Greek%20version%3B%20Hebrew%20reads%20%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%20seer%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20see%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20here%20is%20my%20plan.%20You%20and%20Abiathar%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E15%3A27b%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20lacks%20%3Cem%3Eand%20Abiathar%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20compare%2015%3A29.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20should%20return%20quietly%20to%20the%20city%20with%20your%20son%20Ahimaaz%20and%20Abiathar%26%23x2019%3Bs%20son%20Jonathan.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_15_28%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%2228%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E28%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20will%20stop%20at%20the%20shallows%20of%20the%20Jordan%20River%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E15%3A28%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Eat%20the%20crossing%20points%20of%20the%20wilderness.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20wait%20there%20for%20a%20report%20from%20you.%26%23x201D%3B%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_15_29%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%2229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E29%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20Zadok%20and%20Abiathar%20took%20the%20Ark%20of%20God%20back%20to%20the%20city%20and%20stayed%20there.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_15_30%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%2230%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E30%3C%2Fspan%3EDavid%20walked%20up%20the%20road%20to%20the%20Mount%20of%20Olives%2C%20weeping%20as%20he%20went.%20His%20head%20was%20covered%20and%20his%20feet%20were%20bare%20as%20a%20sign%20of%20mourning.%20And%20the%20people%20who%20were%20with%20him%20covered%20their%20heads%20and%20wept%20as%20they%20climbed%20the%20hill.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_15_31%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%2231%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E31%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20someone%20told%20David%20that%20his%20adviser%20Ahithophel%20was%20now%20backing%20Absalom%2C%20David%20prayed%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BO%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20let%20Ahithophel%20give%20Absalom%20foolish%20advice!%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_15_32%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%2232%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E32%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20David%20reached%20the%20summit%20of%20the%20Mount%20of%20Olives%20where%20people%20worshiped%20God%2C%20Hushai%20the%20Arkite%20was%20waiting%20there%20for%20him.%20Hushai%20had%20torn%20his%20clothing%20and%20put%20dirt%20on%20his%20head%20as%20a%20sign%20of%20mourning.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_15_33%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%2233%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E33%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20David%20told%20him%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BIf%20you%20go%20with%20me%2C%20you%20will%20only%20be%20a%20burden.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_15_34%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%2234%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E34%3C%2Fspan%3EReturn%20to%20Jerusalem%20and%20tell%20Absalom%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BI%20will%20now%20be%20your%20adviser%2C%20O%26%23xA0%3Bking%2C%20just%20as%20I%20was%20your%20father%26%23x2019%3Bs%20adviser%20in%20the%20past.%26%23x2019%3B%20Then%20you%20can%20frustrate%20and%20counter%20Ahithophel%26%23x2019%3Bs%20advice.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_15_35%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%2235%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E35%3C%2Fspan%3EZadok%20and%20Abiathar%2C%20the%20priests%2C%20will%20be%20there.%20Tell%20them%20about%20the%20plans%20being%20made%20in%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20palace%2C%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_15_36%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%2236%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E36%3C%2Fspan%3Eand%20they%20will%20send%20their%20sons%20Ahimaaz%20and%20Jonathan%20to%20tell%20me%20what%20is%20going%20on.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_15_37%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%2237%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E37%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20David%26%23x2019%3Bs%20friend%20Hushai%20returned%20to%20Jerusalem%2C%20getting%20there%20just%20as%20Absalom%20arrived.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_16_1%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2216%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3E2%20Samuel%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EDavid%20and%20Ziba%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20David%20had%20gone%20a%20little%20beyond%20the%20summit%20of%20the%20Mount%20of%20Olives%2C%20Ziba%2C%20the%20servant%20of%20Mephibosheth%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E16%3A1%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cem%3EMephibosheth%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20another%20name%20for%20Merib-baal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20was%20waiting%20there%20for%20him.%20He%20had%20two%20donkeys%20loaded%20with%20200%26%23xA0%3Bloaves%20of%20bread%2C%20100%26%23xA0%3Bclusters%20of%20raisins%2C%20100%26%23xA0%3Bbunches%20of%20summer%20fruit%2C%20and%20a%20wineskin%20full%20of%20wine.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_16_2%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2216%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BWhat%20are%20these%20for%3F%26%23x201D%3B%20the%20king%20asked%20Ziba.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3EZiba%20replied%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BThe%20donkeys%20are%20for%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20people%20to%20ride%20on%2C%20and%20the%20bread%20and%20summer%20fruit%20are%20for%20the%20young%20men%20to%20eat.%20The%20wine%20is%20for%20those%20who%20become%20exhausted%20in%20the%20wilderness.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_16_3%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2216%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BAnd%20where%20is%20Mephibosheth%2C%20Saul%26%23x2019%3Bs%20grandson%3F%26%23x201D%3B%20the%20king%20asked%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BHe%20stayed%20in%20Jerusalem%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20Ziba%20replied.%20%26%23x201C%3BHe%20said%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BToday%20I%20will%20get%20back%20the%20kingdom%20of%20my%20grandfather%20Saul.%26%23x2019%3B%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_16_4%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2216%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BIn%20that%20case%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20the%20king%20told%20Ziba%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BI%20give%20you%20everything%20Mephibosheth%20owns.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BI%20bow%20before%20you%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20Ziba%20replied.%20%26%23x201C%3BMay%20I%20always%20be%20pleasing%20to%20you%2C%20my%20lord%20the%20king.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_16_5%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%